query:
SELECT 
  id,
  projectId,
  totalClients,
  processedClients,
  status,
  startedAt,
  completedAt,
  TIMESTAMPDIFF(MINUTE, startedAt, NOW()) as minutos_decorridos
FROM enrichment_runs
WHERE id = 1;
